      "content": "rebuilding? how can i even talk about rebuilding when the crater is this big? there is no \"ground up\" anymore. every time i close my eyes i just see the numbers and the looks on their faces. it feels like there's no version of the future where this doesn't haunt me. it just feels like a permanent stain.",
